keywords delete
---
Syntax: delete <number>

Deletes a message from a bulletin board in the current room.  You must be
standing in a room that contains a board.  Specify the message number as shown
by the READ or LIST commands.

You may only delete a message if you are the author, a recipient, the clan
leader for a clan board, or an immortal.

See also: NOTE, READ
